data.description: Welcome to your dream home: a Move-in Ready Home on a .12 Acre lot in a serene Cul-De-Sac! This charming property offers modern updates and cozy charm. Inside there's a vaulted living room and dining room. The kitchen with a pantry and nook opens to a covered deck .Upstairs, the main suite features a walk-in closet, while two spare bedrooms offer sitting windows for natural light. Additional features include a utility room with built-ins, an attached two-car garage, and high-efficiency gas water heater for comfort. The newly built shed adds extra storage space. The home boasts new siding, a fenced backyard, and a garden for outdoor enjoyment. Make this your next home.
